#refer to virtual env here http://www.pythonforbeginners.com/basics/how-to-use-python-virtualenv
Create a virtual env: 
virtualenv flask
move to virtualenv : 
cd flask
activate virtualenv:
source bin/activate
now you should see (flask) on the left of the command line. Install flask
pip install flask
Create python file
run python file

Rest of the tutorials from here
https://dzone.com/articles/restful-web-services-with-python-flask
